data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in Denver! This immaculate, like-new 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence is situated conveniently close to the airport, making your daily commute a breeze. Boasting an array of modern features and thoughtful inclusions, this property offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and cutting-edge technology.

Step inside to experience the cozy warmth provided by the central heating system, complemented by refreshing air conditioning for year-round comfort. The tankless water heater ensures an endless supply of hot water, while the pre-wired electric vehicle charger and solar panel setup cater to eco-conscious living.

Your new home is not just modern; it's smart too. Equipped with myQ™ smart garage door opener, Kasa™ smart switches, video doorbell, and a Honeywell T6 Pro Thermostat, you'll enjoy seamless control and monitoring from the palm of your hand.

This property comes fully loaded with high-end appliances, including a refrigerator, dishwasher, microwave, stove/oven, washer, and dryer – all just one year old. The living room is adorned with a 65” Hisense Google Smart TV, while an additional 55” Hisense Google Smart TV graces the upstairs den area. Mounted TVs in select bedrooms, ceiling fans with color temp changeable lights, and bedroom-mounted shelves add a touch of luxury and functionality. 

With garage storage shelving, window blinds, and sliding door vertical blinds already in place, this home is truly move-in ready. Don't miss the chance to make this exceptional property your own – schedule a viewing today and embark on the next chapter of your life in style and comfort!
